or themselves) in order to add a specific dimension (i.e., nurture) to
their general conception of leadership, authority, and pastoral concern"
(^Jesus as Mother~, Univ. of California Press, 1982, p. 149).

	|67-72~. Il velo, ^cinto dalla corona di foglie di olivo~ (|fronde
